{
  "stem": "3631.5",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And until the DP camp, Soldiers of the Palestine Brigade is where Jewish soldiers in the British uniform-- they worked for the British-- the worked for the British Army-- came there to-- to promote people going to Palestine.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And they arranged transports out of Italy into Palestine, some of them illegal.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And they left out of Salzburg.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And we tried to make it to Salzburg.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Another-- another little incident there that-- we left Linz.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "We left Linz.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And the next day, we stood on the street.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Traveling, you stood on the street at the end-- outside-- the outskirts there, and trucks would take you along.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "You'd jump up in the truck.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And after one day, we came to a small town.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they arrested us.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We were waiting for a truck.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They arrested us.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We did not know that-- that a-- a-- a day before, an order was issued that only Austrian citizens were allowed to travel without any permits, and others not.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So they took the four of us, or the eight of us, they put us up in a school.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And that little town, was Wells, W-E-L-L-S.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They kept us there for three days.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They gave us food, and then they put us on the truck and sent us back to Linz.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[CHUCKLES] And after a couple of days, we went by truck from Salzburg.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We went with a truck from Leonding to Salzburg in a transit camp, again, for Austrian, and for Italian, and prisoners.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And we were there for-- for four days-- no, a few days.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And then, we went on by train, to-- supposedly to Italy.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Next morning, we were-- we-- we got a train.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] we were in Munich.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "These were all cattle cars, again, [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And it was raining.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
